      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS timing. This example is mechanically pristine; the critical rod bearing service has been completed using treated shells and ARP hardware, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, sending power to a factory M-variable differential. The suspension remains true to its original geometry with fresh bushings and original-spec damping. Finished in Carbon Black with flawless Nappa leather, this is a turnkey specimen for the purist seeking peak BMW M-division engineering.",
